                <h2 data-uuid="c6e576f0177447e0bddaaf8d7ea1165f">Causes and Effects of the Civil War</h2>
                <p data-uuid="0c5e4aa4c27d407a97029bcd3b616647">Many kinds of differences among Americans led to the Civil War. The long fight had multiple effects on the once-divided people of the United States.</p>
            </article>
